@567899 = ~Can you forge me some elven chain?~
@5678100 = ~Oooh Yes! You likes things hot and spicy? Cespenar stir-fry together some elven chain with some red dragon scales. Add shiitake mushrooms, some andar spices and fire agate peppers and presto: very light, very hot, very filling. Cespenar quite the iron chef ... or perhaps the culinary forger. Unfortunately, special wok and peanut oil will set you back 25,000 gold. You still want?~ [FWCESP43]
